### ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
### Join a meetup (requires auth)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/meetups/{{meetupId}}/join
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
### Unregister from a meetup (requires auth)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/meetups/{{meetupId}}/join
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

